{
  "id": "5cbd8507473aae0017ffbca1",
  "title": "分類と面白さ",
  "created": 1555924236,
  "updated": 1556160806,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5cbd8507473aae0017ffbca1",
      "text": "分類と面白さ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924236,
      "updated": 1555924238
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd8540aff09e0000554c22",
      "text": "面白くない→「なぜ面白くないのか？」→分類しているから？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924288,
      "updated": 1555924365
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd854eaff09e0000554c23",
      "text": "\tKJ法が忌み嫌う「抽象的な概念でとりあえず分類するな！」なのでは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924302,
      "updated": 1555924320
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd8560aff09e0000554c24",
      "text": "\t具体的でないものを分類して2つの具体的でないものに変わる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924320,
      "updated": 1555924334
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd856eaff09e0000554c25",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924335,
      "updated": 1555924335
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd850eaff09e0000554c1e",
      "text": "分類は面白くない(仮説)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924238,
      "updated": 1555924283
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd853baff09e0000554c21",
      "text": "\t「意外な解釈は面白い」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924283,
      "updated": 1555924351
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd857faff09e0000554c26",
      "text": "\t「意外な分類は面白いか？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924351,
      "updated": 1555924357
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd8533aff09e0000554c20",
      "text": "\t「意外な分類は実在するのか？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924275,
      "updated": 1555924390
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd85a6aff09e0000554c27",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924390,
      "updated": 1555924390
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd85a7aff09e0000554c28",
      "text": "分類が面白くない説",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924391,
      "updated": 1555924413
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd85bcaff09e0000554c29",
      "text": "\t1つの軸を天下りで与えて「この軸で考えると2つの対立概念があります」と言うだけ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924413,
      "updated": 1555924658
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd85d1aff09e0000554c2a",
      "text": "\t適当に軸を用意すれば2つの対立概念はできるから対立概念の存在は自明であって面白くない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924433,
      "updated": 1555924673
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd86b7aff09e0000554c36",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924664,
      "updated": 1555924664
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd85d3aff09e0000554c2c",
      "text": "「無茶な軸」を設定して分類するのは楽しい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924436,
      "updated": 1555924446
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd85deaff09e0000554c2d",
      "text": "→「無茶な軸で分類しよう」「無茶だ」→面白くない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924446,
      "updated": 1555924474
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd85faaff09e0000554c2e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924474,
      "updated": 1555924474
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd861caff09e0000554c2f",
      "text": "分類とは「事象に対して問いかけ(=軸)をして「はい」か「いいえ」か「どちらともいえない」の３つに分ける作業",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924509,
      "updated": 1555924516
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd867eaff09e0000554c35",
      "text": "\t分類は「質問をつくる」「質問に答える」の２段階から構成されている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924606,
      "updated": 1555924606
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd8533aff09e0000554c1f",
      "text": "\t分類がつまらないのではなくて、分類が作業になるからつまらない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924275,
      "updated": 1555924542
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd863eaff09e0000554c31",
      "text": "\t「面白くなりうる分類」は分ける際に悩んでしまう分類",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924542,
      "updated": 1555924572
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd865caff09e0000554c32",
      "text": "\t\t言い澱みが発生するような質問のいいよどんだ後の答えが面白い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555924572,
      "updated": 1555924591
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc1211daff09e000068f748",
      "text": "→[分類の裏には問いかけがある]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556160797,
      "updated": 1556163981
    },
    {
      "id": "5cc1211eaff09e000068f749",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1556160798,
      "updated": 1556160798
    }
  ]
}